Package org.gvsig.selectionTools

Class Summary
AboutSelectionToolsExtension Some selection tools for gvSIG of the Consejería de Medio Ambiente de la Junta de Castilla y León.
SelectAllExtension Extension to add support for selecting all the features of a vector layer.
SelectByBufferExtension Extension to add support for selecting the geometries of the active vector layers that intersect with a buffer around their previously selected geometries.
SelectByCircleExtension Extension to add support for selecting the geometries of the active vector layers that intersect with a circle defined by the user.
SelectByPolylineExtension Extension to add support for selecting the geometries of the active vector layers that intersect with a polyline defined by the user.
